  <brief_title>To Investigate the Efficacy and Safety of Vardenafil in Men With Erectile Dysfunction.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised, Double Blind, Placebo Controlled, Multi-center, Fixed Dose, Parallel Group Study to Investigate the Efficacy and Safety of Vardenafil (BAY 38-9456) in Men With Erectile Dysfunction .</official_title>
